he gets up and starts to talk to Arcangel.






Stomper:




"I am Stomper me and five other Maximals have arrived here in a battle 
Crusier but it has been taken apart.

Do you want to help me fix the auto guns?"

"sure!"




in three hours they get six auto guns online.
